a:15:{s:7:"version";s:32:"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1";s:5:"title";s:12:"WeekCRM blog";s:16:"_rss_description";s:355:"Discover the smartest way to choose your next CRM. The WeekCRM blog delivers expert reviews, in-depth comparisons, and curated insights to help startups, sales teams, and solo founders find the perfect CRM without the noise. From beginner-friendly tips to advanced CRM strategies, we simplify your CRM search with real recommendations, no fluff.";s:13:"_rss_language";s:2:"en";s:13:"_itunes_email";s:16:"help@weekcrm.com";s:22:"_itunes_categories_xml";s:0:"";s:13:"_itunes_image";s:74:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/pictures/userpic/userpic-square@2x.jpg?1767535305";s:16:"_itunes_explicit";s:2:"no";s:13:"home_page_url";s:25:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/";s:8:"feed_url";s:29:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/rss/";s:4:"icon";s:67:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/pictures/userpic/userpic@2x.jpg?1767535305";s:7:"authors";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"WeekCRM";s:3:"url";s:25:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/";s:6:"avatar";s:67:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/pictures/userpic/userpic@2x.jpg?1767535305";}}s:5:"items";a:20:{i:0;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:3:"106";s:3:"url";s:94:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/method-crm-surfaces-editable-grid-custom-views-in-app-builder-pr/";s:5:"title";s:70:"Method CRM surfaces Editable Grid custom views in App Builder preview";s:12:"content_html";s:421:"<p>Method shipped an App Builder usability update: when working with Editable Grids, the preview panel now displays custom views, improving build-time preview accuracy.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://forums.method.me/cs/blogs/releasenotes/archive/2026/01/22/method-updates-january-22nd-2026.aspx">https://forums.method.me/cs/blogs/releasenotes/archive/2026/01/22/method-updates-january-22nd-2026.aspx</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-14T13:00:00+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-08T12:55:21+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:10:"method CRM";i:2;s:15:"product updates";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Sat, 14 Feb 2026 13:00:00 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:3:"106";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:1;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:3:"105";s:3:"url";s:93:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/method-crm-fixes-workorder-print-button-error-in-method-classic/";s:5:"title";s:64:"Method CRM fixes WorkOrder print button error in Method Classic";s:12:"content_html";s:382:"<p>Method released a fix for Method Classic where users could hit an unspecified error when loading the WorkOrder print button.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://forums.method.me/cs/blogs/releasenotes/archive/2026/01/26/method-updates-january-26th-2026.aspx">https://forums.method.me/cs/blogs/releasenotes/archive/2026/01/26/method-updates-january-26th-2026.aspx</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-13T13:00:00+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-08T12:52:41+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:10:"method CRM";i:2;s:15:"product updates";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Fri, 13 Feb 2026 13:00:00 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:3:"105";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:2;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:3:"107";s:3:"url";s:92:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/day-ai-adds-loading-status-for-opportunity-context-gathering-2/";s:5:"title";s:61:"Day.ai adds loading status for opportunity context gathering";s:12:"content_html";s:604:"<p>Day.ai published a product update on February 1, 2026.</p>
<p>When viewing newly imported or assistant-created opportunities, users now see a status banner while communication context is still being processed to populate insights. This improves transparency and helps teams understand why some opportunity details may still be loading.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls">https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls</a></p>
