";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-06T20:44:47+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-06T20:44:42+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:10:"method CRM";i:2;s:15:"product updates";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Fri, 06 Feb 2026 20:44:47 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"97";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:10;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"69";s:3:"url";s:71:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/day-ai-tables-now-remember-your-last-view/";s:5:"title";s:41:"Day.ai tables now remember your last view";s:12:"content_html";s:430:"<p>When navigating away from a table and returning, Day.ai restores the last viewed saved view instead of resetting to the default, reducing repeated re-filtering.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls">https://www.day.ai/resources/your-assistant-posts-to-slack-channels-cleaner-tables-floating-meeting-controls</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-06T18:00:00+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-01-28T13:46:26+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:6:"day.ai";i:2;s:15:"product updates";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Fri, 06 Feb 2026 18:00:00 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"69";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:11;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"96";s:3:"url";s:74:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/spiro-separates-merge-and-delete-permissions/";s:5:"title";s:45:"Spiro separates Merge and Delete permissions";s:12:"content_html";s:355:"<p>Spiro now treats merge and delete as distinct permissions. This allows admins to delegate deduplication/cleanup workflows (merge) while restricting irreversible actions (delete).</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-05T21:03:41+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-05T21:03:37+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:15:"product updates";i:2;s:5:"Spiro";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Thu, 05 Feb 2026 21:03:41 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"96";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:12;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"95";s:3:"url";s:74:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/spiro-introduces-a-product-picker-field-type/";s:5:"title";s:45:"Spiro introduces a product picker field type";s:12:"content_html";s:371:"<p>Admins can now use a dedicated product picker field to assign items from the product book to records, expanding how products can be linked across objects beyond traditional quoting/order flows.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-05T21:01:06+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-05T21:01:03+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:15:"product updates";i:2;s:5:"Spiro";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Thu, 05 Feb 2026 21:01:06 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"95";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:13;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"94";s:3:"url";s:77:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/spiro-adds-per-report-fiscal-year-configuration/";s:5:"title";s:47:"Spiro adds per-report fiscal year configuration";s:12:"content_html";s:420:"<p>Reports can now be configured to follow a fiscal calendar by selecting the fiscal year start month within the report settings (Settings → Format). The change applies per report rather than requiring a global setting or custom formulas.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-05T20:56:13+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-05T20:56:10+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:15:"product updates";i:2;s:5:"Spiro";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Thu, 05 Feb 2026 20:56:13 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"94";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:14;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"93";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/spiro-expands-sorting-options-in-pivot-reports/";s:5:"title";s:47:"Spiro expands sorting options in pivot reports";s:12:"content_html";s:378:"<p>Pivot reports now allow sorting across groups using any selected column, not only the row grouping fields. This gives teams more control when ranking results or analyzing distributions across segments.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
";s:14:"date_published";s:25:"2026-02-05T20:54:00+05:00";s:13:"date_modified";s:25:"2026-02-05T20:53:42+05:00";s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;s:3:"CRM";i:1;s:15:"product updates";i:2;s:5:"Spiro";}s:23:"_date_published_rfc2822";s:31:"Thu, 05 Feb 2026 20:54:00 +0500";s:22:"_rss_guid_is_permalink";s:5:"false";s:9:"_rss_guid";s:2:"93";s:15:"_rss_enclosures";a:0:{}s:8:"_e2_data";a:3:{s:12:"is_favourite";b:0;s:14:"links_required";a:0:{}s:9:"og_images";a:0:{}}}i:15;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:2:"92";s:3:"url";s:85:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/spiro-auto-updates-ticket-status-when-manually-assigned/";s:5:"title";s:55:"Spiro auto-updates ticket status when manually assigned";s:12:"content_html";s:376:"<p>If a ticket is moved from Unassigned to a specific user via manual assignment, Spiro now automatically updates the ticket status to Assigned, removing an extra step and keeping queues consistent.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
